  "abstract": "Complete coverage of Anthropic's Claude Managed Agents API: agents, environments, sessions, events, memory stores, vaults, skills attachment, multiagent coordinators, outcomes, webhooks, the `ant` CLI, and the Python/TypeScript SDKs. Includes build/status/test sub-modes, a local-dev playbook with hands-on learnings (vault Bearer-only injection limit, Composio + Asana OAuth quirks, Windows UTF-8, versioning workflow), and 10+ production-proven Python helpers plus curl wrappers.",
